data.description: Discover country living in Cedar Grove - a spacious 4-bed, 2-bath home on 2.53 acres, boasting 2148 square feet. The kitchen is a masterpiece with granite countertops, central island, custom cabinets, and high-end appliances. The master suite offers tranquility with a large walk-in closet. Enjoy panoramic views from expansive decks and cool off in the above-ground pool. This residence combines elegance with comfort, providing a peaceful escape where every day feels like a retreat. Make this property yours!
